STATE
v.
Sebastian X. MOORE. No. 409P05-3. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Sept. 24, 2015. Sebastian X. Moore, Raleigh, for Sebastian X. Moore. Teresa M. Postell, Assistant Attorney General, for State of NC. N. Lorrin Freeman, District Attorney, for State of NC.

Opinion

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 24th of June 2015 by Defendant for Petition for Discretionary Review:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 24th of September 2015."
